        },
        "8015158f-c97f-490e-81d3-3426183423d4": {
          "type": "text",
          "disabled": true,
          "settings": {
            "text": "<p>Hi, I’m Debbie Flohr, and Flohral Preservation is more than my company, it’s my passion and calling. </p><p></p><p>Destiny brought me into this beautiful, creative field. My last name - “Flohr” - means “an array of flowers.” So I guess you could say that I was born for this business! After 17 years in the industry, I’ve pioneered new products and techniques that exemplify Flohral Preservation’s core purpose - to leave you with a lifelong work of art that honors those special moments in your life.</p><p></p><p>When I’m not working, I’m a proud single mother to my 4 boys. I’m blessed and truly OBSESSED with what I do!</p>",
            "text_size": "typeset2",
            "secondary_color": false,
            "enable_highlight": false,
            "highlight_style": "circle"
          }
        },
