            "slide_video_url": "",
            "slide_video_description": "Slide video",
            "heading_size": "h1",
            "heading_tag": "h2",
            "text": "<ul><li>Preserved in full 3D shape & form</li><li>Never pressed. Never reconstructed.</li><li>True-to-life texture & detail</li><li>Captures your bouquet exactly as it was</li><li>Functional, usable home décor</li><li>A modern, timeless aesthetic</li><li>A piece you can hold—not just hang</li><li>An heirloom you can pass down<br/></li></ul><p><em>To have and to hold, Always  & FLOHREVER.</em></p>",
