    "custom_process_cfb9Y6": {
      "type": "custom-process",
      "blocks": {
        "step_HtyP6r": {
          "type": "step",
          "settings": {
            "step_number": "",
            "icon": "shopify://shop_images/4.webp",
            "title": "Save Your Spot for Bouquet Preservation",
            "text": "<p>Secure your date with a deposit to reserve your place in our calendar for your <strong>wedding bouquet preservation</strong>. We only accept a limited number of bouquets each month to ensure each arrangement receives the attention and care it deserves. You’ll finalize your custom keepsake pieces and add-ons only after we receive your flowers.</p>"
          }
        },
        "step_zdXppP": {
          "type": "step",
          "settings": {
            "step_number": "",
            "icon": "shopify://shop_images/6.webp",
            "title": "Send Your Bouquet with Care",
            "text": "<p>After your big day, you simply send your flowers using our step-by-step guide. Once it arrives, we begin the <strong>flower preservation process</strong>, carefully handling every petal with intention, because we know your bouquet holds more than just flowers, it holds memories.</p>"
          }
        },
        "step_rQ8F9g": {
          "type": "step",
          "settings": {
            "step_number": "",
            "icon": "shopify://shop_images/Resin_hexagon.webp",
            "title": "Create Your Custom Keepsake",
            "text": "<p>This is where everything comes together. You’ll be part of the design process as we transform your bouquet into a <strong>custom preserved wedding flower keepsake</strong>. We’ll share design layout options and refine the details with you, creating a piece that feels personal and timeless. Once complete, your <strong>wedding flower preservation piece</strong> arrives ready to display – so you can relive your special day beautifully, for years to come. </p>"
          }
        }
      },
      "block_order": [
        "step_HtyP6r",
        "step_zdXppP",
        "step_rQ8F9g"
      ],
